      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOOKED ON IRAOLA (1) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, finishing in the money last time when 3rd at this track over 400m. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Rates highly and will give a great sight. BRING ON BLING (8) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage a nose away in second (22.36). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from seven attempts. Expected to feature. SPARKY KEY (2) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind George Judy (23.01) in a Grade 5. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Can feature again. THAT'S MINE (3) is always a threat when he races at this track and distance.",
